&gt; &gt; results, although it wasn&#39;t a particularly deceptive task.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; I like the idea of a general method for measuring behavioral
novelty, even
&gt; &gt; if they can be computationally expensive.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; -Drew
